OL,3,CSchool worker banned after lying to
OL,4,Cpupils about having gun and killing
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FA school worker has been banned from
OL,8,Fclassrooms for two years after telling
OL,9,Fpupils he had a gun at home, had
OL,10,Fkilled people, and had the military
OL,11,Fcode name "Kill Switch".
OL,13,FScott John Trigg-Turner, who worked at
OL,14,FBassaleg School in Newport as a
OL,15,Flearning support assistant, knew his
OL,16,Fcomments to a year eight class were
OL,17,Funtrue, abused his position of trust
OL,18,Fand lacked insight into how his
OL,19,Fcomments could have affected pupils, a
OL,20,Fteaching standards hearing was told.
