OL,7,FTrigg-Turner, also a prominent Welsh
OL,8,Finternational wheelchair rugby player
OL,9,Ffor the Wigan Warriors wheelchair
OL,10,Frugby league team, had worked at
OL,11,FBassaleg School from January 2023 on
OL,12,Fsupply and then as staff from
OL,13,FSeptember 2023.
OL,15,FHe resigned in June 2024 after an
OL,16,Finternal investigation.
