OL,7,FThe professional standards panel also
OL,8,Ffound that Trigg-Turner told
OL,9,Fconflicting stories to colleagues
OL,10,Fabout how he came to be a wheelchair
OL,11,Fuser and had shown favouritism to a
OL,12,Fpupil, made a picture for one pupil,
OL,13,Fand on one occasion sat too close to a
OL,14,Fpupil.
OL,16,FHowever, panel chair Helen Beard-
OL,17,FRobbins also criticised Bassaleg
OL,18,FSchool for not holding a formal
OL,19,Fdiscussion when complaints from Trigg-
OL,20,FTurner's colleagues began to mount up.
