OL,7,FHad that been done the LSA might have
OL,8,Fhad the chance to adjust his
OL,9,Fbehaviour, she said.
OL,11,FTrigg-Turner was not present and not
OL,12,Frepresented at the five-day Education
OL,13,FWorkforce Council Wales hearing, which
OL,14,Fbegan on December 3.
OL,16,FThat meant the raft of allegations
OL,17,Fagainst him were taken as denied and
OL,18,Fhe had also denied them during a
OL,19,Fschool investigation, the panel was
OL,20,Ftold.
