OL,7,FTrigg-Turner said to the investigators
OL,8,Fthat his stories to pupils about being
OL,9,Fa killer in the military had been
OL,10,F"misinterpreted".
OL,12,FHe also denied he had poor time
OL,13,Fkeeping at work or that he had shown
OL,14,Ffavouritism to any pupils. He insisted
OL,15,Fhe had behaved professionally at all
OL,16,Ftimes at the school.
