OL,7,FBut the EWC panel, which heard from
OL,8,FTrigg-Turner's colleagues in the
OL,9,FBassaleg School learning support team,
OL,10,Ffound most of the allegations against
OL,11,Fhim proved.
OL,13,FThese included comments to a class of
OL,14,F12 to 13 year-olds that he had been in
OL,15,Fthe military where he had killed
OL,16,Fpeople, although the panel found it
OL,17,Fnot proved that he had said the number
OL,18,Fof people he claimed to have killed
OL,19,Fwas 250.
