OL,12,FReading out the panel's findings,
OL,13,Fpanel chair Helen Beard-Robbins said
OL,14,Fthe committee took on board Trigg-
OL,15,FTurner's previous good record and
OL,16,Fcomments from his colleagues about
OL,17,Fwhat a good LSA he had been.
