OL,7,FHis former colleagues told the hearing
OL,8,Fthat they had enjoyed working with
OL,9,Fhim, he was respected by pupils and
OL,10,Fgood at managing behaviour issues.
OL,11,FThey said he was liked and denied his
OL,12,Fclaims that he had been "singled out".
OL,14,FTrigg-Turner, who went on to work at
OL,15,FCardiff and Vale College after leaving
OL,16,FBassaleg School, was struck off the
OL,17,FEWC register in the categories both of
OL,18,Flearning support worker in schools,
OL,19,Fand FE colleges.
