OL,7,FAnnouncing the decision, Ms Beard-
OL,8,FRobbins said his lapses were
OL,9,F"sustained and deliberate" and not
OL,10,Fisolated incidents.
OL,12,F"There is evidence of deep seated
OL,13,Fattitudinal problems given the lies
OL,14,FTrigg-Turner told pupils, colleagues,
OL,15,Fand his line manager," she said,
OL,16,Fadding: "He has not engaged with this
OL,17,Fhearing and his limited engagement
OL,18,Fshows an unwillingness to resolve
OL,19,Fmatters."
